---
import RegisterButton from './RegisterButton.astro';
---
<section class="section">
  <div class="container text-block" style="text-align: center;">
    <h2>The <span class="highlight">biggest enrolment opportunity</span> in private school marketing right now is <span class="highlight">Facebook Ads.</span></h2>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6;">
      Facebook Ads is the most powerful enrolment engine a private school can build.
      Targeted to one parent at a time, in your local area, on their phone. You find
      out what problem they want solved for their child, then show them ads about that
      exact problem - every week, for the full 3-12 months they take to decide. You
      nurture them, you speed up the decision, and you're there when they're ready to
      enrol. Businesses have been doing this for over a decade. Almost no school has
      been shown the process. <strong>This webinar fixes that.</strong>
    </p>
    <div style="margin-top: var(--space-xl);">
      <RegisterButton label="Register for the Webinar" />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
